1
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,948
<font color="#FFFFFF">Eric.</font>

2
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:21,033
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ragnar Lothbrok,
welcome to my house.</font>

3
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">You also, Rollo.</font>

4
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've done as you asked, Ragnar,</font>

5
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,754
<font color="#FFFFFF">and sought out these
young men to meet you.</font>

6
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:32,758
<font color="#FFFFFF">All of them have sworn upon their
rings to keep this meeting a secret.</font>

7
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,991
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have done well, my friend,</font>

8
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">although I knew
I could trust you.</font>

9
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:40,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are we here for?</font>

10
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,593
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are here, firstly,</font>

11
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:45,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">because you have
nothing better to do.</font>

12
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:49,878
<font color="#FFFFFF">See, all you lot live
idle and wasted lives.</font>

13
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,233
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen to him!</font>

14
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have built a new boat.</font>

15
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,229
<font color="#FFFFFF">A boat?</font>

16
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:59,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">And with this boat,
for the first time,</font>

17
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,194
<font color="#FFFFFF">we can go west.</font>

18
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:06,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">Across the great sea
to a place called England,</font>

19
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,758
<font color="#FFFFFF">where countless riches await us.</font>

20
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:11,912
<font color="#FFFFFF">How would we steer
across the open sea?</font>

21
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:16,633
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have discovered a way.</font>

22
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">You want us to join
you in the boat?</font>

23
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,756
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, we do.</font>

24
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:24,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I have Ragnar's word
that we will all be equal</font>

25
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">and share equally
the spoils of our raid.</font>

26
00:02:26,719 --> 00:02:28,120
<font color="#FFFFFF">If there are any.</font>

27
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is your name?</font>

28
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">Knut.</font>

29
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:40,277
<font color="#FFFFFF">I promise you, Knut,
I've heard witnesses.</font>

30
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:42,074
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just stories.</font>

31
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:44,312
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Just stories."</font>

32
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,194
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Just stories"?</font>

33
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:53,877
<font color="#FFFFFF">All things begin
and end as stories.</font>

34
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have to remember, though,</font>

35
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:59,111
<font color="#FFFFFF">that Earl Haraldson has
ordered us to sail east.</font>

36
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:02,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Earl knows nothing
about our new boat.</font>

37
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">He knows nothing about the
new way of navigating.</font>

38
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:08,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is why he refuses
to let us go west.</font>

39
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,756
<font color="#FFFFFF">He could kill us
for disobeying his orders.</font>

40
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, he could.</font>

41
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:17,675
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can offer you
a chance to shine in battle</font>

42
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,633
<font color="#FFFFFF">and impress the gods,</font>

43
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:24,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">and to bring back such plunder
that you have never seen before.</font>

44
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:30,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you got
the balls to join us?</font>

45
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll go.</font>

46
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,120
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I. I will go.</font>

47
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,389
<font color="#FFFFFF">I, too! I will, too!</font>

48
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I! I will go!</font>

49
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">What about you, Knut?</font>

50
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you coming?</font>

51
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:58,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, I want a good story
to tell my children.</font>

52
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,879
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah!</font>

53
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:03,116
<font color="#FFFFFF">Prepare to leave
in the next few weeks,</font>

54
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:06,028
<font color="#FFFFFF">and tell no one
that doesn't need to know.</font>

55
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,955
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good throw.</font>

56
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,439
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well played.</font>

57
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,589
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well?</font>

58
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,875
<font color="#FFFFFF">My Lord, there was a meeting.</font>

59
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,589
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where?</font>

60
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">In the house of Eric Marteinn.</font>

61
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">Was Ragnar Lothbrok there?</font>

62
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Lord.</font>

63
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,678
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shall we show them the ax?</font>

64
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:44,872
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nothing would please me
more, but it's too soon.</font>

65
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to watch and wait.</font>

66
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,553
<font color="#FFFFFF">Only good things
come from watching</font>

67
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,439
<font color="#FFFFFF">and waiting.</font>

68
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,112
<font color="#FFFFFF">Were you looking at my wife?</font>

69
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:21,160
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you slept with her?</font>

70
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,276
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, Lord!</font>

71
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:25,273
<font color="#FFFFFF">I swear on all the gods.</font>

72
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:30,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">If she wants to sleep with you,</font>

73
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:32,798
<font color="#FFFFFF">then I give my permission.</font>

74
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,997
<font color="#FFFFFF">It will all be arranged.</font>

75
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">So when do we sail?</font>

76
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,879
<font color="#FFFFFF">I already told you.</font>

77
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want you to come.</font>

78
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,754
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why not?</font>

79
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:13,358
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need to leave
the children and the farm</font>

80
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:15,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">in the hands of someone I trust.</font>

81
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:19,031
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if the Earl finds out we
have gone without his permission?</font>

82
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:21,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">He might try
and claim our family home.</font>

83
00:06:22,879 --> 00:06:26,668
<font color="#FFFFFF">This was going to be the most
exciting voyage of our lives.</font>

84
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,793
<font color="#FFFFFF">To go west!</font>

85
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:37,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have dreamed of it many times,</font>

86
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:42,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">and in my dreams,
we are always together.</font>

87
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,437
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if there is no west?</font>

88
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:51,870
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is the most dangerous
and stupid voyage ever.</font>

89
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:56,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if we both die, hmm?</font>

90
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:59,235
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then who would take
care of the children?</font>

91
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">Rollo?</font>

92
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,791
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have no right to say that!</font>

93
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right, all right.</font>

94
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">You go.</font>

95
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,040
<font color="#FFFFFF">You go</font>

96
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:24,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I shall stay here
and look after the children.</font>

97
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:31,194
<font color="#FFFFFF">Siggy?</font>

98
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go away!</font>

99
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:40,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's so cold in here,</font>

100
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">but we'll be warm soon enough.</font>

101
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do you take me for?</font>

102
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:12,999
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you really suppose
that a worm like you</font>

103
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,877
<font color="#FFFFFF">could sleep
with a woman like me?</font>

104
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,757
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm an earl's wife!</font>

105
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:28,716
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now I know who to trust</font>

106
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,752
<font color="#FFFFFF">and who not to trust.</font>

107
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take him. Yes, Lord.</font>

108
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:39,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get rid of him.</font>

109
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:42,080
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come. Go where?</font>

110
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Outside.</font>

111
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get up!</font>

112
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,196
<font color="#FFFFFF">My love!</font>

113
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:45,077
<font color="#FFFFFF">Never mind that.
Defend yourself.</font>

114
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,668
<font color="#FFFFFF">How dare you!</font>

115
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">Am I not good enough for you?</font>

116
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,831
<font color="#FFFFFF">Am I not strong enough for you?</font>

117
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,875
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen...</font>

118
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">You listen.</font>

119
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:16,398
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't you remember?
I saved your life.</font>

120
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">How could I forget?</font>

121
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,235
<font color="#FFFFFF">You keep reminding me.</font>

122
00:10:40,039 --> 00:10:41,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm so angry with you!</font>

123
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop!</font>

124
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:50,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you mad? You could
have killed each other!</font>

125
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that what you want?</font>

126
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">We were just having an argument.</font>

127
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:55,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, never argue
like that again.</font>

128
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:58,475
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go on then! Back to bed!</font>

129
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:02,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">Huh.</font>

130
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:10,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a fine thing</font>

131
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:13,831
<font color="#FFFFFF">when the little pig
teaches the boar a lesson.</font>

132
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:31,793
<font color="#FFFFFF">Olafur surprised me.</font>

133
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:35,437
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't think, out of all of
them, he would behave like that.</font>

134
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">A man lives
or dies by his honor.</font>

135
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:39,835
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's true.</font>

136
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">He thought so little of mine</font>

137
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:44,871
<font color="#FFFFFF">that he really believed
that I would give you to him?</font>

138
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:50,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">Honor is a rare
commodity these days.</font>

139
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes.</font>

140
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:55,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">Almost as rare as those
in whom I can trust.</font>

141
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:59,629
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's true, my love,
our enemies are everywhere.</font>

142
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Everywhere"?</font>

143
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">They cannot prevail.</font>

144
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:19,236
<font color="#FFFFFF">They cannot prevail.</font>

145
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,712
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you still angry with me?</font>

146
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

147
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:40,835
<font color="#FFFFFF">But my heart is in still such
pain that I cannot be with you.</font>

148
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">Rollo.</font>

149
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:13,158
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nice work, Eric.</font>

150
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:27,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where is my anchor?</font>

151
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:29,676
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was promised for today.</font>

152
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,118
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maybe your blacksmith is a liar.</font>

153
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,032
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, I don't think so.</font>

154
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">This hair is from
his daughter's head.</font>

155
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:42,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">I promised him that if he
went to Earl Haraldson,</font>

156
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:44,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would find a way to kill her.</font>

157
00:13:52,799 --> 00:13:54,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">I still don't see Knut.</font>

158
00:13:54,919 --> 00:13:57,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, that's because
he isn't here.</font>

159
00:13:57,759 --> 00:13:59,797
<font color="#FFFFFF">He hasn't sent word either.</font>

160
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">That troubles me.</font>

161
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,196
<font color="#FFFFFF">We live in a sea of troubles.</font>

162
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:12,875
<font color="#FFFFFF">But look, some are ended.</font>

163
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here, this is yours.</font>

164
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:23,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">And this is mine.</font>

165
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">Master.</font>

166
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:17,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">May the gods bless us with
powerful winds and calm seas.</font>

167
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come here, slave.</font>

168
00:17:02,879 --> 00:17:05,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cover the ravens.</font>

169
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:09,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Feel that wind.
That breeze is up.</font>

170
00:17:15,559 --> 00:17:17,551
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ready the oars!</font>

171
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come.</font>

172
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,388
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well?</font>

173
00:18:17,039 --> 00:18:18,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">They have set sail.</font>

174
00:18:18,799 --> 00:18:21,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good. They'll never
be heard from again.</font>

175
00:18:21,759 --> 00:18:22,910
<font color="#FFFFFF">But...</font>

176
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,670
<font color="#FFFFFF">But what?</font>

177
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:29,635
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if Ragnar is right?</font>

178
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:33,157
<font color="#FFFFFF">There are no lands to the west!</font>

179
00:18:38,039 --> 00:18:39,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get out.</font>

180
00:18:45,039 --> 00:18:46,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's noon.</font>

181
00:18:47,599 --> 00:18:48,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look at the board.</font>

182
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,034
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get the bucket.</font>

183
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not too far south.</font>

184
00:19:15,079 --> 00:19:16,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nor too far north.</font>

185
00:19:19,759 --> 00:19:21,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">The board works.</font>

186
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">How do we know?</font>

187
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,993
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah.</font>

188
00:19:32,519 --> 00:19:35,797
<font color="#FFFFFF">The great sea is held
in place by Jörmungand,</font>

189
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,109
<font color="#FFFFFF">the serpent,</font>

190
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:40,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">whose giant body encircles it,</font>

191
00:19:40,359 --> 00:19:44,273
<font color="#FFFFFF">and who keeps his tail in his
mouth to complete the circle</font>

192
00:19:44,359 --> 00:19:46,431
<font color="#FFFFFF">and stop
the waves breaking loose.</font>

193
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:53,197
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>But one day, the god
Thor, son of earth,</i></font>

194
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:55,556
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>was fishing in the sea
for the serpent,</i></font>

195
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:58,200
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>using a bull's head for bait.</i></font>

196
00:19:59,279 --> 00:20:03,672
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Jörmungand reared up and the
waves pummeled the shore</i></font>

197
00:20:03,759 --> 00:20:06,719
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>as he twisted
and writhed in a fury.</i></font>

198
00:20:09,839 --> 00:20:13,151
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>They were well matched,
serpent and god,</i></font>

199
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:15,071
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>in that furious fight.</i></font>

200
00:20:18,519 --> 00:20:21,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">The seas boiled around them,</font>

201
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:25,676
<font color="#FFFFFF">but then the hook
became dislodged,</font>

202
00:20:26,039 --> 00:20:28,111
<font color="#FFFFFF">and the serpent slithered free</font>

203
00:20:29,319 --> 00:20:33,472
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and sank again, so quickly,
beneath the waves.</i></font>

204
00:20:36,119 --> 00:20:40,193
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And soon, the sea
was calm once more,</i></font>

205
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:43,440
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>as if nothing had disturbed it.</i></font>

206
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,513
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thor.</font>

207
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">Storm's coming.</font>

208
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">Should we let down the sail?</font>

209
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:07,797
<font color="#FFFFFF">Floki, should we
let down the sail?</font>

210
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, we have
to take the sail down,</font>

211
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,798
<font color="#FFFFFF">and then we must row.</font>

212
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,598
<font color="#FFFFFF">If we are not moving forward,</font>

213
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:16,511
<font color="#FFFFFF">then we will be soaked
by the waves and sink.</font>

214
00:21:16,599 --> 00:21:17,715
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ready?</font>

215
00:21:17,799 --> 00:21:20,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep her straight!
You heard him!</font>

216
00:21:33,319 --> 00:21:34,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tent!</font>

217
00:21:46,759 --> 00:21:48,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shove the oars!</font>

218
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Row!</font>

219
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:51,874
<font color="#FFFFFF">Row!</font>

220
00:22:46,759 --> 00:22:48,432
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you afraid?</font>

221
00:22:48,799 --> 00:22:52,919
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Ragnar Lothbrok,
I am afraid.</font>

222
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:55,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">But not for me.</font>

223
00:22:56,759 --> 00:22:58,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am afraid for my boat.</font>

224
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:06,276
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thor is striking his anvil.</font>

225
00:23:06,759 --> 00:23:08,830
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is angry with us.</font>

226
00:23:09,359 --> 00:23:11,477
<font color="#FFFFFF">He wants to sink us.</font>

227
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's true!</font>

228
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:27,151
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thor is beating his hammer.</font>

229
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:30,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">The lightning is the
sparks from his anvil.</font>

230
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">But he's not angry with us.</font>

231
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,318
<font color="#FFFFFF">I understand now.</font>

232
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why should he be angry with us?</font>

233
00:23:37,119 --> 00:23:40,477
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why should he want
to sink our boat?</font>

234
00:23:40,559 --> 00:23:43,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't you understand?
He is celebrating.</font>

235
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is full of good news.</font>

236
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:49,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">He wants to show everybody
that he can't sink this boat.</font>

237
00:23:50,039 --> 00:23:51,598
<font color="#FFFFFF">He loves this boat!</font>

238
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:53,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sit down, you idiot!</font>

239
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:57,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's my boat,
and the gods love my boat.</font>

240
00:23:57,359 --> 00:23:58,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why should I</font>

241
00:23:59,519 --> 00:24:01,397
<font color="#FFFFFF">not be happy?</font>

242
00:24:01,839 --> 00:24:04,513
<font color="#FFFFFF">Floki, sit down.</font>

243
00:24:05,039 --> 00:24:07,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">Remember, you can't swim!</font>

244
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">Father Cuthbert!</font>

245
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:10,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is it, Brother Athelstan?</font>

246
00:25:10,799 --> 00:25:12,314
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can all see the signs.</font>

247
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,710
<font color="#FFFFFF">Signs? What signs?
Of what do you speak?</font>

248
00:25:14,799 --> 00:25:18,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know as well as we
that judgment day is at hand.</font>

249
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,834
<font color="#FFFFFF">Jeremiah says so!</font>

250
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:21,798
<font color="#FFFFFF">"And on that day,
the sun shall be darkened,"</font>

251
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:23,472
<font color="#FFFFFF">"and the moon shall
not give her light,"</font>

252
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:25,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">"and the stars
of heaven shall fall."</font>

253
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:27,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">In the name of God,
that is enough.</font>

254
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:28,954
<font color="#FFFFFF">But it's true!</font>

255
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:31,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">"And I stood upon
the sand of the sea,"</font>

256
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:33,511
<font color="#FFFFFF">"and saw a beast
rise up out of the sea,"</font>

257
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:36,035
<font color="#FFFFFF">"having seven
heads and 10 horns."</font>

258
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:37,473
<font color="#FFFFFF">I will hear no more!</font>

259
00:25:37,559 --> 00:25:39,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">You will return
to your dormitory</font>

260
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:42,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">and pray to God for
forgiveness and humility.</font>

261
00:25:42,559 --> 00:25:45,677
<font color="#FFFFFF">And when the storm has
passed, all shall be well.</font>

262
00:25:45,799 --> 00:25:48,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">You will do as I order.</font>

263
00:25:51,759 --> 00:25:52,796
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Father.</font>

264
00:26:49,359 --> 00:26:52,318
<font color="#FFFFFF">There is no west!</font>

265
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:02,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are not sailing
towards any new country,</font>

266
00:27:03,039 --> 00:27:07,114
<font color="#FFFFFF">but just into an empty ocean,</font>

267
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:14,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">utterly and completely lost.</font>

268
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:19,909
<font color="#FFFFFF">Kauko, Leif, we have been
persuaded by madmen and fools.</font>

269
00:27:22,559 --> 00:27:25,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">The god Loki
is behind this voyage.</font>

270
00:27:26,759 --> 00:27:30,070
<font color="#FFFFFF">That scoundrel, that sly one.</font>

271
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:32,915
<font color="#FFFFFF">Trouble and suffering
are meat and drink to him.</font>

272
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,319
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shut up, man! No!</font>

273
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:36,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

274
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:39,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">If anyone is mad, it is you.</font>

275
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:43,316
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not the one who convinced
all these good men</font>

276
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:47,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">to sacrifice their lives
for a dream, an illusion.</font>

277
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:50,753
<font color="#FFFFFF">It wasn't me who joined
forces with The Sly One</font>

278
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:52,751
<font color="#FFFFFF">to get us to sail west</font>

279
00:27:53,039 --> 00:27:55,919
<font color="#FFFFFF">into nothing, into nowhere.</font>

280
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,991
<font color="#FFFFFF">- He's mad!
- Don't tempt the gods!</font>

281
00:27:58,079 --> 00:28:01,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, and here we are, lost,</font>

282
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">certain to die.</font>

283
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,032
<font color="#FFFFFF">For what?</font>

284
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:09,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sit down and shut up.</font>

285
00:28:09,119 --> 00:28:11,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">You sound like The Sly One.</font>

286
00:28:11,279 --> 00:28:13,077
<font color="#FFFFFF">Perhaps you are
the god of mischief</font>

287
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:15,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">who sends men mad and sends
them to their deaths.</font>

288
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:16,516
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sit down!</font>

289
00:28:16,599 --> 00:28:20,276
<font color="#FFFFFF">I curse the day I ever agreed to
come with you, Ragnar Lothbrok.</font>

290
00:28:20,359 --> 00:28:23,353
<font color="#FFFFFF">For this ship is cursed,
and we are...</font>

291
00:28:40,279 --> 00:28:41,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">Release the ravens.</font>

292
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:01,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">If the birds do not return,
there is land.</font>

293
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">But if they do...</font>

294
00:29:12,279 --> 00:29:13,279
<font color="#FFFFFF">Father!</font>

295
00:29:18,079 --> 00:29:19,833
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good day to you, blacksmith.</font>

296
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:26,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">My Lord, how can I be
of use to you?</font>

297
00:29:28,519 --> 00:29:30,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">You make anchors, don't you?</font>

298
00:29:31,359 --> 00:29:32,359
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, Lord.</font>

299
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:36,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you made any recently?</font>

300
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,199
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, not recently,
Lord Haraldson.</font>

301
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:45,794
<font color="#FFFFFF">You didn't forge an anchor for
a man called Ragnar Lothbrok?</font>

302
00:29:49,039 --> 00:29:50,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would have remembered.</font>

303
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't hurt my daughter.</font>

304
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why would I hurt your daughter?</font>

305
00:29:58,200 --> 00:30:00,509
<font color="#FFFFFF">His Lordship just wants
to know the truth.</font>

306
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:04,270
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you forge the anchor
for Ragnar Lothbrok's ship?</font>

307
00:30:12,359 --> 00:30:14,238
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, I forged it.</font>

308
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:16,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go of her.</font>

309
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,200
<font color="#FFFFFF">Put down your hammer.</font>

310
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">I promise you no harm
will come to your daughter.</font>

311
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look in the flames.</font>

312
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:45,358
<font color="#FFFFFF">The sages say that
we can see our future</font>

313
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:49,519
<font color="#FFFFFF">in the flames.</font>

314
00:31:01,119 --> 00:31:02,236
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

315
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:04,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please, no!</font>

316
00:31:04,279 --> 00:31:05,430
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do you see?</font>

317
00:31:05,519 --> 00:31:07,192
<font color="#FFFFFF">I see my own death.</font>

318
00:31:08,039 --> 00:31:11,112
<font color="#FFFFFF">No! No!</font>

319
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:15,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

320
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">They've come back.</font>

321
00:31:36,319 --> 00:31:37,640
<font color="#FFFFFF">There's no land.</font>

322
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">Seabirds!</font>

323
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">Seagulls!</font>

324
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Seagulls?</font>

325
00:31:46,519 --> 00:31:47,839
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen!</font>

326
00:31:50,359 --> 00:31:51,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whoo-hoo!</font>

327
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,758
<font color="#FFFFFF">It works! Yeah!</font>

328
00:31:57,839 --> 00:31:59,115
<font color="#FFFFFF">We made it!</font>

329
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:03,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">Row! We made it! Row!</font>

330
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ragnar, you did it!</font>

331
00:33:00,079 --> 00:33:01,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tie the sail!</font>

332
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oars! Drop the oars!</font>

333
00:33:19,039 --> 00:33:20,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is it?</font>

334
00:33:20,359 --> 00:33:22,238
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why was the warning bell rung?</font>

335
00:33:22,359 --> 00:33:24,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">They've come. They are here.</font>

336
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:26,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who is here?</font>

337
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,959
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hell and all its devils!</font>

338
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:33,517
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lock the doors and stay
inside, all of you! Hurry.</font>

339
00:33:34,519 --> 00:33:35,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">The gate!</font>

340
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:48,436
<font color="#FFFFFF">They know we're here.</font>

341
00:33:49,759 --> 00:33:52,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">No one throw their lives
away unnecessarily,</font>

342
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,919
<font color="#FFFFFF">even to impress the gods.</font>

343
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stay close.</font>

344
00:34:13,039 --> 00:34:15,077
<font color="#FFFFFF">They're here! Come, Brother!</font>

345
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,195
<font color="#FFFFFF">Quick!</font>

346
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">Arne, get to work.</font>

347
00:35:01,079 --> 00:35:02,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't be afraid.</font>

348
00:35:03,199 --> 00:35:04,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Trust in God,</font>

349
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:07,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">and let us pray.</font>

350
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is the end!</font>

351
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Son of Man cometh!</font>

352
00:36:40,679 --> 00:36:41,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get away!</font>

353
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leif.</font>

354
00:37:56,079 --> 00:37:57,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah!</font>

355
00:38:53,119 --> 00:38:54,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't understand.</font>

356
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:57,389
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why do they leave such
treasures unprotected?</font>

357
00:38:57,599 --> 00:39:01,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is there some spell, some
magic which protects them?</font>

358
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">It appears not.</font>

359
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:08,079
<font color="#FFFFFF">Perhaps they think
their god protects them.</font>

360
00:39:09,639 --> 00:39:12,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">If this is their god,
then he's dead.</font>

361
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is nailed to a cross.</font>

362
00:39:14,559 --> 00:39:15,880
<font color="#FFFFFF">He cannot protect anyone.</font>

363
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:18,429
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is not alive,
like Odin, Thor or Freyr.</font>

364
00:39:19,039 --> 00:39:20,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">What use is he then?</font>

365
00:39:39,679 --> 00:39:41,273
<font color="#FFFFFF">You speak our language?</font>

366
00:39:44,159 --> 00:39:46,072
<font color="#FFFFFF">How do you speak our language?</font>

367
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:48,193
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've traveled.</font>

368
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are told to travel,
to take the word of God.</font>

369
00:39:51,559 --> 00:39:54,757
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please, don't kill me.</font>

370
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:08,436
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is that you
have in your hand?</font>

371
00:40:10,159 --> 00:40:11,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">A book.</font>

372
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">The gospel of St. John,
I wanted to save it.</font>

373
00:40:22,079 --> 00:40:24,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">Of all the treasures
I see in this place,</font>

374
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:27,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">you chose to save this?</font>

375
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:29,829
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes.</font>

376
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hmm.</font>

377
00:40:32,639 --> 00:40:33,869
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why?</font>

378
00:40:39,639 --> 00:40:40,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why?</font>

379
00:40:43,119 --> 00:40:47,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because without the word of
God, there is only darkness.</font>

380
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:01,356
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is a strange place indeed.</font>

381
00:41:02,719 --> 00:41:05,791
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have been everywhere
and we have found no women.</font>

382
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just these strange men.</font>

383
00:41:09,719 --> 00:41:12,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">I believe they are the
priests of their god.</font>

384
00:41:13,679 --> 00:41:15,114
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take what you will.</font>

385
00:41:15,239 --> 00:41:17,436
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is what we came for.</font>

386
00:41:19,719 --> 00:41:21,791
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why have you not
killed this one?</font>

387
00:41:22,239 --> 00:41:24,117
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is worth more alive</font>

388
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,034
<font color="#FFFFFF">to sell as a slave.</font>

389
00:41:26,119 --> 00:41:27,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">I will kill him.</font>

390
00:41:27,679 --> 00:41:29,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">We have no room
left on the boat.</font>

391
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:31,398
<font color="#FFFFFF">I forbid it.</font>

392
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">How can you forbid it,
little brother?</font>

393
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:36,197
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are all equals,</font>

394
00:41:37,559 --> 00:41:38,994
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I say he dies.</font>

395
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:46,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">Does it really mean
that much to you, brother?</font>

396
00:42:03,639 --> 00:42:06,757
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is what
we care for your god.</font>

397
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:44,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">So much gold!</font>

398
00:43:44,679 --> 00:43:45,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look!</font>

399
00:43:46,760 --> 00:43:48,193
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep them moving!</font>

400
00:43:59,119 --> 00:44:00,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your doing, Floki?</font>

401
00:44:37,639 --> 00:44:38,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">Want to drown, my friend?</font>

402
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:40,639
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me help you.</font>

